00:49:22.501 --> 00:49:23.961
Point. Front kick.

1057
00:49:23.961 --> 00:49:26.423
What are you looking at?
Finish him!

1058
00:49:26.423 --> 00:49:28.425
[UTTERING KARATE CRY]

1059
00:49:28.425 --> 00:49:29.508
Return.

1060
00:49:32.720 --> 00:49:34.180
Prepare.

1061
00:49:34.180 --> 00:49:35.390
<i>Hei!</i>

1062
00:49:37.516 --> 00:49:39.894
We do not train
to be merciful here.

1063
00:49:39.894 --> 00:49:41.812
Mercy is for the weak.

1064
00:49:41.812 --> 00:49:44.899
Here, on the street,
in competition,

1065
00:49:44.899 --> 00:49:46.943
a man confronts you,
he is the enemy.

1066
00:49:46.943 --> 00:49:48.652
An enemy deserves no mercy.

1067
00:49:48.652 --> 00:49:51.072
What is the problem,
Mr. Lawrence?

1068
00:49:51.072 --> 00:49:52.449
[INAUDIBLE DIALOGUE]

1069
00:49:54.242 --> 00:49:56.453
Hey, come on, let's forget this.

1070
00:49:56.453 --> 00:49:58.413
Wait. Not yet.

1071
00:50:00.748 --> 00:50:03.918
Class, we have visitors.
Fall in behind me.<i> Hei!</i>

1072
00:50:11.092 --> 00:50:14.053
