1074
00:50:17.223 --> 00:50:19.100
Are you calling
Mr. Lawrence a liar?

1075
00:50:19.100 --> 00:50:21.394
No call no one nothing.

1076
00:50:21.394 --> 00:50:23.562
What are you here for, old man?

1077
00:50:23.562 --> 00:50:26.316
Come ask leave boy alone.

1078
00:50:26.316 --> 00:50:27.650
What's the matter?

1079
00:50:27.650 --> 00:50:29.402
