of his own problems?

1080
00:50:29.402 --> 00:50:31.528
One-to-one problem, yes.

1081
00:50:31.528 --> 00:50:34.949
Five-to-one problem,
too much ask anyone.

1082
00:50:34.949 --> 00:50:37.660
