The odds?

1083
00:50:37.660 --> 00:50:39.662
Well, we can fix that.

1084
00:50:39.662 --> 00:50:41.289
Feel like matching,
Mr. Lawrence?

1085
00:50:41.289 --> 00:50:42.499
Yes, sensei!

1086
00:50:42.499 --> 00:50:43.916
No more fighting.

1087
00:50:43.916 --> 00:50:46.710
This is a karate dojo,
not a knitting class.

1088
00:50:46.710 --> 00:50:48.045
You don't come in my dojo

1089
00:50:48.045 --> 00:50:50.298
