and leave, old man.

1090
00:50:50.298 --> 00:50:51.590
Now, get your boy on the mat,

1091
00:50:51.590 --> 00:50:53.510
or you and I will have
a major problem.

1092
00:50:53.510 --> 00:50:56.304
Too much advantage, your dojo.

1093
00:50:57.888 --> 00:50:59.349
Name a place.

1094
00:50:59.932 --> 00:51:01.267
Tournament.

1095
00:51:01.267 --> 00:51:02.477
[SNICKERING]

1096
00:51:05.688 --> 00:51:08.691
You got real nerve, old man.
Real nerve.

1097
00:51:10.151 --> 00:51:12.862
But I think
we can accommodate you.

1098
00:51:12.862 --> 00:51:14.905
Can't we, Mr. Lawrence?

1099
00:51:14.905 --> 00:51:16.282
Yes, sensei.

1100
00:51:16.866 --> 00:51:18.284
Fall in.

1101
00:51:22.955 --> 00:51:26.083
Ask one more small request.

1102
00:51:26.083 --> 00:51:27.668
Make it fast.

1103
00:51:27.668 --> 00:51:30.587
Ask leave boy alone to train.

1104
00:51:31.964 --> 00:51:34.300
You're a pushy little bastard,
ain't you?

1105
00:51:34.300 --> 00:51:36.469
But I like that.
I like that.

1106
00:51:38.929 --> 00:51:40.515
All right.

1107
00:51:40.515 --> 00:51:42.933
No one touches the prima donna
until the tournament.

1108
00:51:43.684 --> 00:51:45.019
Is that understood?

1109
00:51:45.019 --> 00:51:46.479
ALL:
Yes, sensei!

1110
00:51:48.605 --> 00:51:50.191
But you don't show...

1111
00:51:52.068 --> 00:51:53.652
and it's open season...

1112
00:51:55.279 --> 00:51:56.613
on him...

1113
00:51:58.575 --> 00:51:59.783
and you.

1114
00:52:26.352 --> 00:52:28.605
I can't believe this.

1115
00:52:28.605 --> 00:52:29.813
I cannot believe this.

1116
00:52:29.813 --> 00:52:31.232
What?

1117
00:52:31.232 --> 00:52:32.983
What you just got
me into in there. Huh?

1118
00:52:32.983 --> 00:52:34.818
You said you would
make things better for me.

1119
00:52:34.818 --> 00:52:36.529
That I did.
How?

1120
00:52:36.529 --> 00:52:40.866
How? Just save you
two-month beating.

1121
00:52:40.866 --> 00:52:42.285
Oh, great. I can't wait.

1122
00:52:42.285 --> 00:52:44.370
Now I really got something
to look forward to.

1123
00:52:48.958 --> 00:52:51.794
DANIEL: How much longer
till we get to your house?

1124
00:52:51.794 --> 00:52:53.588
MIYAGI:
Hmm, other side tracks.

1125
00:52:53.588 --> 00:52:55.881
What, are you... What, are you
in the oil business too?

1126
00:52:55.881 --> 00:52:57.174
[MIYAGI LAUGHING]

1127
00:52:57.174 --> 00:52:59.927
Not everything is as seem.

1128
00:52:59.927 --> 00:53:01.512
Ha, this place
reminds me of Newark.

1129
00:53:01.512 --> 00:53:02.597
What are we gonna do here?

1130
00:53:02.597 --> 00:53:04.140
We start training.

1131
00:53:04.140 --> 00:53:06.016
MIYAGI:
Much work be done.

1132
00:53:06.016 --> 00:53:08.727
Tournament here
before you know it.

1133
00:53:08.727 --> 00:53:10.813
DANIEL: Yeah. That's
what I'm afraid of.

1134
00:53:14.233 --> 00:53:16.611
Man, that teacher
was really wacko.

1135
00:53:16.611 --> 00:53:18.112
Hmm.

1136
00:53:18.112 --> 00:53:19.822
You really think
I'm gonna beat that guy?

1137
00:53:19.822 --> 00:53:21.698
Ah, no matter.

1138
00:53:21.698 --> 00:53:24.160
Wacko teacher
attitude rest in fist.

1139
00:53:24.160 --> 00:53:28.289
Stupid, but fact of life.
Win, lose, no matter.

1140
00:53:28.289 --> 00:53:31.250
You make good fight.
Earn respect.

1141
00:53:31.250 --> 00:53:32.793
Then nobody bother.

1142
00:53:32.793 --> 00:53:34.671
Yeah. They'll bury me
where I fall.

1143
00:53:34.671 --> 00:53:35.712
[CHUCKLES]

1144
00:53:35.712 --> 00:53:38.174
Either way, problem solved.

1145
00:53:38.174 --> 00:53:39.883
Wait right here.

1146
00:53:45.931 --> 00:53:47.475
[CROWS CAWING]

1147
00:53:48.892 --> 00:53:50.436
This is great.

1148
00:53:56.025 --> 00:53:58.068
MIYAGI:
Hey!

1149
00:53:58.068 --> 00:54:00.446
Oh, Mr. Miyagi, I forgot to give
this back to you last night.

1150
00:54:00.446 --> 00:54:02.072
No, no, no, you keep.

1151
00:54:02.072 --> 00:54:03.073
Oh, thanks a lot.

1152
00:54:03.073 --> 00:54:05.117
So ready?

1153
00:54:05.117 --> 00:54:06.827
Yeah, I guess so.

1154
00:54:07.411 --> 00:54:08.745
[SIGHS]

1155
00:54:08.745 --> 00:54:09.955
[METAL CLANKING]

1156
00:54:09.955 --> 00:54:11.540
Daniel-san, must talk.

1157
00:54:14.292 --> 00:54:16.461
Walk on road, hmm.

1158
00:54:16.461 --> 00:54:21.466
Walk right side, safe.
Walk left side, safe.

1159
00:54:21.466 --> 00:54:23.510
Walk middle, sooner or later...

1160
00:54:23.510 --> 00:54:25.011
[MIMICS GRAPE
GETTING SQUISHED]

1161
00:54:25.011 --> 00:54:27.639
Get squished just like grape.

1162
00:54:27.639 --> 00:54:31.642
Here karate, same thing.
Either you karate do, yes,

1163
00:54:32.560 --> 00:54:34.769
or karate do, no.

1164
00:54:34.769 --> 00:54:36.771
You karate do, "guess so",

1165
00:54:36.771 --> 00:54:38.315
[MIMICS GRAPE
GETTING SQUISHED]

1166
00:54:38.315 --> 00:54:39.650
Just like grape.

1167
00:54:40.359 --> 00:54:41.735
Understand?

1168
00:54:43.194 --> 00:54:44.779
Yeah, I understand.

1169
00:54:45.863 --> 00:54:47.240
Now ready?

1170
00:54:48.408 --> 00:54:50.117
Yeah, I'm ready.

1171
00:54:50.117 --> 00:54:51.369
Yes.

1172
00:54:53.746 --> 00:54:55.998
Must make sacred pact.

1173
00:54:57.625 --> 00:55:01.420
I promise to teach karate.
That my part.

1174
00:55:02.421 --> 00:55:04.632
You promise learn.

1175
00:55:04.632 --> 00:55:07.884
I say, you do. No question.

1176
00:55:08.594 --> 00:55:10.094
That your part.

1177
00:55:11.346 --> 00:55:13.014
Deal?

1178
00:55:13.014 --> 00:55:14.516
It's a deal.

1179
00:55:14.516 --> 00:55:15.684
Yes.

1180
00:55:19.771 --> 00:55:24.149
First, wash all the car.
Then wax. Wax...

1181
00:55:24.149 --> 00:55:25.984
Why do I have to wax...
Uh, uh, uh.

1182
00:55:25.984 --> 00:55:28.445
Remember deal.
No question.

1183
00:55:28.445 --> 00:55:30.113
Yeah, but I...
Right!

1184
00:55:30.113 --> 00:55:31.532
Huh.

1185
00:55:31.532 --> 00:55:36.620
Wax on, right hand.
Wax off, left hand.

1186
00:55:36.620 --> 00:55:40.206
Wax on. Wax off.

1187
00:55:40.206 --> 00:55:43.376
Breathe in through nose,
out the mouth.

1188
00:55:43.376 --> 00:55:44.502
[INHALES AND EXHALES]

1189
00:55:44.502 --> 00:55:47.463
Wax on, wax off.

1190
00:55:47.463 --> 00:55:50.424
Don't forget to breathe.
