1191
00:55:50.424 --> 00:55:53.552
Wax on, wax off.

1192
00:55:53.552 --> 00:55:55.929
Wax on, wax off.

1193
00:55:55.929 --> 00:55:57.640
Hey, where did these cars
come from?

1194
00:55:57.640 --> 00:56:01.727
Wax on. Detroit. Wax off.

1195
00:56:01.727 --> 00:56:05.021
Wax on. Wax off.

1196
00:56:05.021 --> 00:56:06.523
[SIGHS]

1197
00:56:17.241 --> 00:56:19.034
No, no, no.

1198
00:56:19.034 --> 00:56:23.163
Wax on.
Right hand, make circle.

1199
00:56:23.163 --> 00:56:26.416
Wax off. Left hand, circle.

1200
00:56:26.416 --> 00:56:29.419
Wax on. Wax off.

1201
00:56:29.419 --> 00:56:32.631
Breathe in. Breathe out.

1202
00:56:32.631 --> 00:56:35.592
Wax on. Wax off.

1203
00:56:36.133 --> 00:56:37.343
Ah.

1204
00:56:37.343 --> 00:56:40.388
Wax on. Wax off.

1205
00:56:40.388 --> 00:56:43.474
Wax on. Wax off.

1206
00:57:09.123 --> 00:57:11.166
Hey, Mr. Miyagi,
I'm finished.

1207
00:57:12.668 --> 00:57:14.670
Hey, you want
to check these out?

1208
00:57:15.838 --> 00:57:16.921
Mr. Miyagi?

1209
00:57:16.921 --> 00:57:18.131
[KNOCKS]

1210
00:57:19.174 --> 00:57:20.509
Mr. Miyagi?

1211
00:57:23.678 --> 00:57:25.346
Mr. Miyagi?

1212
00:57:27.390 --> 00:57:28.850
Hello?

1213
00:57:30.184 --> 00:57:31.227
Mr...

1214
00:57:40.193 --> 00:57:41.445
[SNORING]

1215
00:57:59.587 --> 00:58:01.380
[PEOPLE CHATTERING]

1216
00:58:01.380 --> 00:58:02.924
[BELL RINGING]

1217
00:58:04.966 --> 00:58:06.218
Hey, there you are.

1218
00:58:06.218 --> 00:58:07.969
I've been looking
all over for you today.

1219
00:58:07.969 --> 00:58:09.012
Where you been?

1220
00:58:09.012 --> 00:58:10.096
I don't believe it.

1221
00:58:10.096 --> 00:58:12.098
What? Hey,
where're you going?

1222
00:58:12.098 --> 00:58:13.767
I'm gonna go
find that idiot, Daniel.

1223
00:58:13.767 --> 00:58:15.059
It's gonna stop.
No, relax.

1224
00:58:15.059 --> 00:58:16.436
Everything's been taken care of.

1225
00:58:16.436 --> 00:58:17.813
Oh, yeah.
Until next time?

1226
00:58:17.813 --> 00:58:19.397
No, there isn't gonna be
a next time.

1227
00:58:19.397 --> 00:58:20.815
There they are.

1228
00:58:20.815 --> 00:58:22.483
What? All right.
Watch this.

1229
00:58:22.483 --> 00:58:24.694
Hey, guys. How you doin'?
It's good to see you.

1230
00:58:24.694 --> 00:58:26.529
Hey, sorry about
the eye there, Johnny.

1231
00:58:26.529 --> 00:58:27.655
Your shoulder okay, Tommy?

1232
00:58:27.655 --> 00:58:29.323
You guys be careful

1233
00:58:29.323 --> 00:58:31.575
not to go step in front of
any more buses now, all right?

1234
00:58:31.575 --> 00:58:33.744
Hold it.
Remember what sensei said?

1235
00:58:33.744 --> 00:58:35.329
You got to wait
for the tournament.

1236
00:58:35.329 --> 00:58:37.581
Must be
take-a-worm-for-a-walk week!

1237
00:58:39.959 --> 00:58:41.752
You did all that damage?

1238
00:58:41.752 --> 00:58:43.754
Like, you know, when you
make a wish in a shower

1239
00:58:43.754 --> 00:58:44.921
it always comes true?

1240
00:58:44.921 --> 00:58:46.297
I should have kept
my mouth shut.

1241
00:58:46.297 --> 00:58:47.883
No, no, no.
We got an agreement.

1242
00:58:47.883 --> 00:58:49.676
Oh, yeah? What's that?

1243
00:58:49.676 --> 00:58:51.552
Well, they agreed
not to beat up on me,

1244
00:58:51.552 --> 00:58:52.845
and I promised
not to get my blood

1245
00:58:52.845 --> 00:58:55.055
