I don't know...

1294
01:00:55.293 --> 01:00:56.962
Oh, those are my parents.

1295
01:00:56.962 --> 01:00:58.630
Come on, come on.
I want you to meet 'em.

1296
01:00:58.630 --> 01:00:59.798
Oh, great.

1297
01:01:00.465 --> 01:01:01.549
Hello, sweetheart.

1298
01:01:01.549 --> 01:01:03.051
Hey, Dad.

1299
01:01:03.051 --> 01:01:04.969
Um, Mom and Dad,
